title: A TIME LAPSE trip down Market Street, San Francisco, 1906

sources.title: A TIME LAPSE trip down Market Street, San Francisco, 1906
sources.description: This is a time compressed, 16:9 formatted, color hues and foley sound effects added version of the famous "a trip down market street" film. Music is Sony Vegas score and is used under license. You are legally free to re-mix the video portion of this clip.
